Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.08,0:01:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類因人口膨脹而向宇宙移民已過了半個世紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.23,0:01:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球周圍漂浮著巨大的人工都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為人類的「第二故鄉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.86,0:01:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們就在這裏出生、成長、生兒育女\N並走向死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙世紀0079年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.83,0:02:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離地球最遠的宇宙都市SIDE 3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以ZION公國之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向地球聯邦政府發起了獨立戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在開始一個月的戰鬥裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.77,0:02:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION公國和地球聯邦軍有半數以上的人口死去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.84,0:02:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們對於自己的行為產生了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭由此進入膠著狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷時八個多月……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.53,0:02:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『GUNDAM挺立大地！！』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.83,0:03:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史立達，你留在這裏等我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，曹長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.33,0:04:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曹長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍事設施似在右面建築物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是上班時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.83,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但只見一部車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.88,0:04:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連一個人也看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.15,0:04:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見了，是個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.69,0:04:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早餐還未吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.07,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早知會是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.93,0:04:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不吃早餐會餓壞身體的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉，阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉，阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉你看來很精神呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Thank you，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，你準備穿什麼出去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.85,0:05:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我修理好計算機之後便會去吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你沒有聽到避難命令嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避難命令？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那警號嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真氣人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.73,0:05:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒聽到軍方廣播嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍艦入港所以要到避難所啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不知道啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請各位快到避難所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在對面等你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈囉 跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.08,0:05:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.58,0:05:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可以這樣？是鄰居啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不通知阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說避難的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.39,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！只有他一人仍留在家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.29,0:05:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...如果沒阿姆羅爸爸的軍方技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.13,0:05:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們又怎會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們是因為要建設研究基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要大家搬，你還生氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是這個意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.23,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.18,0:06:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！真沒禮貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.35,0:06:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸是否在將入港的軍艦上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.09,0:06:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一星期前說會從地球回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏會成為戰場嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸甚麼也沒跟我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將White Base的零件盡快搬到母艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫技工們快手一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.65,0:06:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想不到White Base會被ZION跟蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦？這個就是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是我們聯邦軍的新銳母艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.66,0:06:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艦和GUNDAM完成的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要打敗ZION國便輕而易舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報告，我們已到達SIDE 7
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請盡快到艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字是布萊特？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你加入軍隊有多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十九歲嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到GUNDAM可以量產時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們這些少年就不用上戰場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時戰爭也都結束了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你的兒子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.58,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，聽說你們這年紀的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都要加入游擊隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，據說是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，雷上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.19,0:07:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這母艦終也逃不出敵人的追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是遺憾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來我的運氣真壞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然在作戰完畢回航途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇上這件獵物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.32,0:08:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又或者是他們的運氣好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，夏亞少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是在這偏僻的衛星內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.63,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有聯邦軍的V作戰計劃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能他們在開發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我們的ZAKU更優秀的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧！這偏僻的衛星...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒有消息回來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暗號是C.C.2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看！我的預測證實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.41,0:08:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那即是說聯邦已有機動戰士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.79,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該說是開發並且己成功了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三台也是機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.03,0:09:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來裏面還有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是攻擊的最好時機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的任務只在於偵察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但被他們裝上戰艦之後便...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.14,0:09:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必急於爭功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占！你想幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞少校不也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打勝了仗才陞官的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想違抗命令？快停手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我立了大功便可出人頭地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打敗敵人是越快動手越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.99,0:10:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在附近的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種震動的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.64,0:10:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是ZION軍的攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去找爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.91,0:10:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你出去會為我們添麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.28,0:10:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸是軍人，這裏不能持久的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看能否到軍艦裏避難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.36,0:10:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.17,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請關上門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION國的機動戰士！
